metadata.name: City Evening by Tenth Key 2/21
metadata.description: The streets light up at night. City Evening by Tenth Key is a deep house remix of City Morning that captures the other side of a city. The sun has gone down, street lights and neon signs light up the night and create a more hypnotic atmosphere. The people at the bars and restaurants and dance clubs are more relaxed and enjoying themselves. There are good times to be had beneath those city lights, and they invite you to join in. Holders of this unique NFT will receive whitelist access and discounts to future Tenth Key music drops, plus one free mint to a future drop.
